573
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] i samo se pravimo

574
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:24,259
[SPEAKER_01] kao da to ne postoji.

575
00:25:24,259 --> 00:25:27,660
