578
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] oni koji su izvan crkve.

579
00:25:33,079 --> 00:25:34,779
[SPEAKER_01] Nama nisu problem

580
00:25:34,779 --> 00:25:36,279
[SPEAKER_01] oni koji su izvan crkve,

581
00:25:36,279 --> 00:25:37,039
[SPEAKER_01] koji napadaju.

582
