584
00:25:42,220 --> 00:25:44,140
[SPEAKER_01] Vi znate onu staru usporedbu.

585
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne tone brod

586
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] zbog vode koja je oko njega.

587
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:52,160
[SPEAKER_01] Brod tone zbog vode koja je u njemu.

588
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu problem oni što pljuju

589
00:25:56,500 --> 00:25:58,180
[SPEAKER_01] koji su van naše crkve.

590
00:25:58,180 --> 00:25:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] Njih će biti.

591
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] Njih i treba biti.

592
00:26:01,079 --> 00:26:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] Jer htijeli ili ne htijeli,

593
00:26:03,119 --> 00:26:04,200
[SPEAKER_01] ako živimo svoju vjeru,

594
00:26:04,200 --> 00:26:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] doći ćemo u sukob.

595
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:07,220
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne možete brati tratinčice

596
00:26:07,220 --> 00:26:08,319
[SPEAKER_01] i hodati biti kršćani.

597
00:26:08,319 --> 00:26:10,819
[SPEAKER_01] To ne ide jedno s drugim.

598
00:26:11,900 --> 00:26:13,519
[SPEAKER_01] Nužno ćete doći u sukob.

599
00:26:13,519 --> 00:26:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ali problem je

600
00:26:15,039 --> 00:26:17,200
[SPEAKER_01] kada mi između sebe ratujemo.

601
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] Kada smo mi posvađani.

602
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] Kada se nas hoće razdijeliti

603
00:26:21,940 --> 00:26:25,220
[SPEAKER_01] i okrenuti jedno protiv drugoga.

604
00:26:25,220 --> 00:26:26,579
[SPEAKER_01] E to je tužno.

605
00:26:26,579 --> 00:26:27,640
[SPEAKER_01] To je žalosno.

606
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] I to najviše boli.

607
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] I to je ta voda koja je unutar broda

608
00:26:31,579 --> 00:26:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] koji to ne.

609
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:37,839
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što je sve više i više.

610
00:26:37,839 --> 00:26:40,200
[SPEAKER_01] Nije problem ništa okolo.

611
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] Problem smo mi iznutra.

612
00:26:41,900 --> 00:26:44,440
[SPEAKER_01] I tako je potrebno posvijestiti

613
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:45,759
[SPEAKER_01] i ja i vi

614
00:26:45,759 --> 00:26:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] da smo ti i ja crkva.

615
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:51,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam crkva, ti si crkva.

616
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam problem, ti si problem.

617
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:57,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam rješenje, ti si rješenje.

618
00:26:57,279 --> 00:26:59,240
[SPEAKER_01] Da to nije netko drugi i treći

619
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] nego da smo to mi.

620
00:27:01,319 --> 00:27:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] I na kraju vidimo kako ne možemo reći crkvi ne,

621
00:27:08,420 --> 00:27:09,660
[SPEAKER_01] a Isusu da.

622
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:12,940
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što je Isus ustanovio crkvu.

623
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:14,460
[SPEAKER_01] On ju je htio takvu.

624
00:27:14,460 --> 00:27:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] Isus je htio crkvu.

625
00:27:16,099 --> 00:27:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo grešni.

626
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je Isus htio crkvu koja je sveta.

627
00:27:20,119 --> 00:27:22,259
[SPEAKER_01] Pozvao je 12 apostola.

628
00:27:23,079 --> 00:27:24,640
[SPEAKER_01] Je li Isus mogao odabrati ljude

629
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] koji su savršeni,

630
00:27:25,539 --> 00:27:26,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji će biti uz njega

631
00:27:26,940 --> 00:27:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] i neće ga ni izdati,

632
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:29,640
[SPEAKER_01] ni otići od njega,

633
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:30,339
[SPEAKER_01] ni napustiti.

634
00:27:30,339 --> 00:27:32,200
[SPEAKER_01] Apsolutno je mogao.

635
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:34,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ali Isus zbira učenike.

636
00:27:34,359 --> 00:27:36,859
[SPEAKER_01] Plan, svi su bili kukavice na kraju.

637
00:27:36,859 --> 00:27:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan ostao.

638
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj ga zatajio.

639
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ali Isus im je oprostio.

640
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] Isto je tako s nama.

641
00:27:44,500 --> 00:27:46,740
[SPEAKER_01] Pas ćemo tisuću puta.

642
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne mojemo misliti

643
00:27:48,579 --> 00:27:50,220
[SPEAKER_01] da smo daleko od Boga,

644
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:51,220
[SPEAKER_01] da nas Bog ne voli.

645
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:53,740
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono što djavao želi da mislite.

646
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:56,660
[SPEAKER_01] Isus nas poziva u zajednicu.

647
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:58,640
[SPEAKER_01] Isus nam želi oprostiti više

648
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego što ti sam sebi želiš oprostiti.

649
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] I toliko je možda stvari i grijeha

650
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] koje non stop nam se vraćaju na pamet.

651
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pusti to.

652
00:28:06,380 --> 00:28:08,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je ispovjeđeno,

653
00:28:08,059 --> 00:28:10,279
[SPEAKER_01] to pusti Bogu.

654
00:28:10,279 --> 00:28:12,140
[SPEAKER_01] Živi danas.

655
00:28:13,019 --> 00:28:13,819
[SPEAKER_01] Opet ponavljam,

656
00:28:13,819 --> 00:28:16,240
[SPEAKER_01] nemoj kopati po prošlosti.

657
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:18,599
[SPEAKER_01] Prekrasno mi je bilo

658
00:28:18,599 --> 00:28:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] kad je Isus govorio Savlu u viđenju

659
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] Savle, Savle, zašto me progoniš?

660
00:28:28,539 --> 00:28:31,799
[SPEAKER_01] Nije govorio zašto progoniš moje kršćane,

661
00:28:31,799 --> 00:28:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] nego je govorio zašto me progoniš.

662
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,680
[SPEAKER_01] O čemu se to uradi?

663
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:41,660
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo progonili Isusa u tim kršćanima.

664
00:28:42,539 --> 00:28:44,019
[SPEAKER_01] Kasnije Isus kaže,

665
00:28:44,019 --> 00:28:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] što god učiniste jednome od moje najmanje braće,

666
00:28:47,380 --> 00:28:48,700
[SPEAKER_01] meni učiniste.

667
00:28:48,700 --> 00:28:50,900
[SPEAKER_01] Doslovno Isusu učiniste.

668
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže,

669
00:28:52,019 --> 00:28:53,980
[SPEAKER_01] bijah goli za odijenu ste me,

670
00:28:53,980 --> 00:28:57,819
[SPEAKER_01] bijah u tamnici i posjetili ste me.

671
00:28:57,819 --> 00:28:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] Sve što ste učinili,

672
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:02,140
[SPEAKER_01] jednom od najmlađe moje braće,

673
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:03,700
[SPEAKER_01] meni ste učinili.

674
00:29:04,539 --> 00:29:09,339
[SPEAKER_01] I tu Isus doslovno govori da je dio crkve,

675
00:29:09,339 --> 00:29:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] da je crkva.

676
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:13,779
[SPEAKER_01] I nije biblijski reći crkvi da,

677
00:29:13,779 --> 00:29:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] Kristu da,

678
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] a crkvi ne.

679
00:29:17,019 --> 00:29:19,400
[SPEAKER_01] jer je to isprepleteno.

680
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,799
[SPEAKER_01] Što nam je činiti?

681
00:29:21,799 --> 00:29:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] Kod nas je velik problem nerazumijevanja.

682
00:29:24,940 --> 00:29:27,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nešto ne upoznaš,

683
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:30,799
[SPEAKER_01] ne možeš ne vidjeti da je nešto važno.

684
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:32,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se sjećam,

685
00:29:32,299 --> 00:29:33,339
[SPEAKER_01] kod nas u samostanu,

686
00:29:33,339 --> 00:29:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] ovo sam spominjao,

687
00:29:34,420 --> 00:29:38,140
[SPEAKER_01] bio je jedan časni brat.

688
00:29:38,140 --> 00:29:40,119
[SPEAKER_01] To vam je kod časna sestra samo muško.

689
00:29:40,119 --> 00:29:41,259
[SPEAKER_01] Logično.

690
00:29:41,259 --> 00:29:44,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je najbolje objašnjenje ikad.

691
00:29:44,339 --> 00:29:45,279
[SPEAKER_01] Časni brat.

692
00:29:45,279 --> 00:29:47,799
[SPEAKER_01] I on je čuo kako je jedan naš fratar

693
00:29:47,799 --> 00:29:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] otišao u studiji na Rim,

694
00:29:49,539 --> 00:29:51,319
[SPEAKER_01] u Rim, na studiji.

695
00:29:51,319 --> 00:29:53,240
[SPEAKER_01] I pita,

696
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:55,279
[SPEAKER_01] pa što je on otišao?

697
00:29:55,279 --> 00:29:57,420
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, otišao u Rim.

698
00:29:57,420 --> 00:29:58,839
[SPEAKER_01] Pa što će raditi tamo?

699
00:29:58,839 --> 00:29:59,640
[SPEAKER_01] Pa studirat će.

700
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:01,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, pa što će studirat?

701
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:02,640
[SPEAKER_01] Liturgiku.

702
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, pa šta to ima studirat?

703
00:30:05,539 --> 00:30:07,140
[SPEAKER_01] Upališ sviće,

704
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] kažeš misu,

705
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,839
[SPEAKER_01] ugasiš sviće.

706
00:30:09,839 --> 00:30:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] Njemu je to bilo dovoljno.

707
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:15,380
[SPEAKER_01] On je sve tu misu vidio

708
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:16,980
[SPEAKER_01] na tako jednostavan način

709
00:30:16,980 --> 00:30:18,799
[SPEAKER_01] da upališ sviće,

710
00:30:18,799 --> 00:30:20,220
[SPEAKER_01] slaviš misu,

711
00:30:20,220 --> 00:30:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] ugasiš sviće.

712
00:30:21,039 --> 00:30:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] Šta to ima študirat?

713
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,599
[SPEAKER_01] I druga stvar

714
00:30:24,599 --> 00:30:26,720
[SPEAKER_01] koju ja stalno prepričavam,

715
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ovako smotan u čeljade dosta.

716
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] Mi na humcu,

717
00:30:30,579 --> 00:30:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] na humcu uz muzej,

718
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:34,579
[SPEAKER_01] smo imali lapidari

719
00:30:34,579 --> 00:30:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] i u tom lapidariji su oni veliki ostaci,

720
00:30:37,980 --> 00:30:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] nadgrobni spomenici.

721
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:43,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam otišao to malo počistiti.

722
00:30:43,259 --> 00:30:45,440
[SPEAKER_01] Vidim dolje neke kamenčiće,

723
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] tu hrpica ovdje,

724
00:30:47,119 --> 00:30:47,640
[SPEAKER_01] hrpica,

725
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,660
[SPEAKER_01] bože moj,

726
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] opet su nešto razbacali

727
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:51,140
[SPEAKER_01] i ništa.

728
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uzmem metlu,

729
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] uzmem kantu,

730
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:53,980
[SPEAKER_01] pometem,

731
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:55,240
[SPEAKER_01] to je te sve kamenčiće

732
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:56,700
[SPEAKER_01] i sve stavim u jednu kantu,

733
00:30:56,700 --> 00:30:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] reku,

734
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] ako im bude trebalo,

735
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:58,640
[SPEAKER_01] tu je.

736
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] I dolazi ovaj arheolog,

737
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad je on to vidio.

738
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:05,819
[SPEAKER_01] čovjeku se tlakovi sastali.

739
00:31:07,819 --> 00:31:10,160
[SPEAKER_01] Svaka ta hrpica je bilo stoljeće.

740
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:14,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam njemu to počistio.

741
00:31:14,599 --> 00:31:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to bila nakupina kamenčića

742
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:20,839
[SPEAKER_01] koji tu stoje,

743
00:31:20,839 --> 00:31:22,299
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne mogu proći smetaju mi,

744
00:31:22,299 --> 00:31:24,299
[SPEAKER_01] a njemu su to bila stoljeća.

745
00:31:24,299 --> 00:31:26,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam njemu nekih 500, 600 godina

746
00:31:26,799 --> 00:31:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] smeo u jednu kantu

747
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] da mu je to na jednom mjestu.

748
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjeku nije dobro bilo.

749
00:31:31,579 --> 00:31:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

750
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:35,980
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što ja te stvari ne kužim.

751
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to kamen,

752
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] njemu je to vrijedni nalaz.

753
00:31:39,039 --> 00:31:40,799
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se to kaže?

754
00:31:40,799 --> 00:31:42,920
[SPEAKER_01] Vrijedni nešto.

755
00:31:42,920 --> 00:31:43,720
[SPEAKER_01] Kamen.

756
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ali upravo zato što ja

757
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:49,559
[SPEAKER_01] ne razumijem,

758
00:31:49,559 --> 00:31:50,839
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam o tome dovoljno,

759
00:31:50,839 --> 00:31:52,680
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu to ni znati cijeniti.

760
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:55,019
[SPEAKER_01] Isto je tako o svetoj misi

761
00:31:55,019 --> 00:31:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] i o crkvi.

762
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:58,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ne upoznajemo svetu misu,

763
00:31:58,460 --> 00:32:00,579
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne upoznajemo svoju crku,

764
00:32:00,579 --> 00:32:02,700
[SPEAKER_01] nećemo je moći dovoljno

765
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] ni voljeti, ni cijeniti.

766
00:32:04,599 --> 00:32:07,119
[SPEAKER_01] i samo ćemo se lijepiti

767
00:32:07,119 --> 00:32:09,259
[SPEAKER_01] na ove vijesti,

768
00:32:09,259 --> 00:32:11,779
[SPEAKER_01] na ovu žutu štampu

769
00:32:11,779 --> 00:32:13,460
[SPEAKER_01] i na sve ono što nam iskoči.

770
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:15,559
[SPEAKER_01] Vi znate da

771
00:32:15,559 --> 00:32:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] nijedna dobra stvar nije vijest.

772
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:19,200
[SPEAKER_01] Rijedko kad ćete čuti

773
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,640
[SPEAKER_01] da je nešto pozitivno.

774
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] Antunovski hod.

775
00:32:22,119 --> 00:32:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] Više ćeš stvari vidjeti

776
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:27,160
[SPEAKER_01] o negativnim situacijama

777
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] nego nešto što je prekrasno

778
00:32:28,460 --> 00:32:29,180
[SPEAKER_01] kao vaš hod

779
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] i ostale stvari koje radite.

780
00:32:30,599 --> 00:32:33,240
[SPEAKER_01] I tako isto s nama svećenicima.

781
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:36,160
[SPEAKER_01] Vi znate da tisuće aviona lete,

782
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije da nije vijest

783
00:32:38,619 --> 00:32:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] nego onaj koji se srušio.

784
00:32:42,119 --> 00:32:43,660
[SPEAKER_01] Kad raste cijela šuma,

785
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:45,259
[SPEAKER_01] to se ništa ne čuje.

786
00:32:45,259 --> 00:32:46,819
[SPEAKER_01] Cijela šuma izrasla

787
00:32:46,819 --> 00:32:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] bez ikakvog zvuka.

788
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:49,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad jedno drvo padne,

789
00:32:49,859 --> 00:32:51,339
[SPEAKER_01] to si tekako čuje.

790
00:32:51,339 --> 00:32:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ima prekrasnih svetih svećenika.

791
00:32:54,460 --> 00:32:56,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ima svetih ljudi...

792
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao sam svetih.

793
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] Šalim se.

794
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:04,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ima svetih ljudi koji žive,

795
00:33:04,359 --> 00:33:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] koji su predani Bogu.

796
00:33:06,019 --> 00:33:08,240
[SPEAKER_01] I nemojte dopustiti

797
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] da vam jedna mrlja

798
00:33:10,519 --> 00:33:13,299
[SPEAKER_01] zamagli cijeli pogled.

799
00:33:13,299 --> 00:33:14,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se sjećam,

800
00:33:14,799 --> 00:33:16,980
[SPEAKER_01] jedan je svećenik molio

801
00:33:16,980 --> 00:33:19,400
[SPEAKER_01] kako želi postati proziran.

802
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] Niči veze što se postati proziran.

803
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:22,779
[SPEAKER_01] Glupo.

804
00:33:22,779 --> 00:33:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad malo bolje razmislim,

805
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:27,180
[SPEAKER_01] možda nešto najveće,

806
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] što jedan svećenik može napraviti

807
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:30,819
[SPEAKER_01] je postati proziran.

808
00:33:30,819 --> 00:33:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] Da ljudi više ne vide tebe,

809
00:33:33,220 --> 00:33:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] nego da vide Krista.

810
00:33:35,380 --> 00:33:37,700
[SPEAKER_01] I možemo se pitati,

811
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] jesam li ja nekome prepreka do Boga?

812
00:33:40,079 --> 00:33:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam li ja nekome poticaj

813
00:33:42,599 --> 00:33:44,940
[SPEAKER_01] ili spoticaj do Boga?

814
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,319
[SPEAKER_01] Jao meni,

815
00:33:46,319 --> 00:33:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] ako neko zbog mene napusti crkvu,

816
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] ali blago meni,

817
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,799
[SPEAKER_01] ako neko zbog mene uzljubi

818
00:33:51,799 --> 00:33:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] više Krista.

819
00:33:52,940 --> 00:33:55,160
[SPEAKER_01] I isto je tako pitanje

820
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] za sve nas ovdje.

821
00:33:57,119 --> 00:33:58,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je svatko od nas crkva,

822
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] kakav ja primjer dajem

823
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:04,200
[SPEAKER_01] kao crkva?

824
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:05,900
[SPEAKER_01] Je li ljudi zbog mene

825
00:34:05,900 --> 00:34:08,219
[SPEAKER_01] požele upoznati moga Boga

826
00:34:08,219 --> 00:34:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] ili ljudi zbog mene

827
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:12,059
[SPEAKER_01] požele otići

828
00:34:12,059 --> 00:34:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] iz crkve?

829
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] na kraju

830
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:18,719
[SPEAKER_01] Prastjepan vam je govorio

831
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:20,139
[SPEAKER_01] o ispovjedi,

832
00:34:20,139 --> 00:34:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] o molitvi.

833
00:34:21,579 --> 00:34:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ima jedan stari tekst

834
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:26,039
[SPEAKER_01] koji je govorio o pobožnosti

835
00:34:26,039 --> 00:34:27,820
[SPEAKER_01] i o duhovnosti.

836
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] I stavio bih vam uistinu na srce

837
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:32,679
[SPEAKER_01] da budete i pobožni

838
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:33,780
[SPEAKER_01] i duhovni.

839
00:34:34,219 --> 00:34:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] nije isto biti pobožan

840
00:34:35,559 --> 00:34:36,920
[SPEAKER_01] i biti duhovan.

841
00:34:37,780 --> 00:34:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pobožnost je sredstvo

842
00:34:39,579 --> 00:34:41,440
[SPEAKER_01] a duhovnost je cilj.

843
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:44,519
[SPEAKER_01] pobožnost se može postići

844
00:34:44,519 --> 00:34:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] disciplinom.

845
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan,

846
00:34:46,579 --> 00:34:47,559
[SPEAKER_01] trš, trš, trš, trš,

847
00:34:47,559 --> 00:34:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] to tako, tako i tako.

848
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ti ćeš izgledati pobožan.

849
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:52,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako ta pobožnost

850
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] ne mijenja tvoju nutrinu,

851
00:34:53,539 --> 00:34:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] ti nikad nećeš postati duhovan.

852
00:34:55,579 --> 00:34:57,139
[SPEAKER_01] Samo ćeš ploviti.

853
00:34:57,139 --> 00:34:58,480
[SPEAKER_01] Plutati.

854
00:34:58,480 --> 00:35:00,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to volim usporediti

855
00:35:00,139 --> 00:35:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] sa plastičnom bocom.

856
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:03,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ako vi zatvorite plastičnu bocu

857
00:35:03,559 --> 00:35:04,820
[SPEAKER_01] i bacite je na more,

858
00:35:04,820 --> 00:35:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] u more,

859
00:35:05,619 --> 00:35:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] ona će cijeli svoj život

860
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:08,059
[SPEAKER_01] samo plutati.

861
00:35:08,059 --> 00:35:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako joj otvorite čep,

862
00:35:09,860 --> 00:35:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] ona će potonuti

863
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] i pašće lijepo na dno.

864
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] Napunit će se vodom.

865
00:35:14,119 --> 00:35:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] Isto je tako nam.

866
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mi možemo dolaziti,

867
00:35:17,079 --> 00:35:17,739
[SPEAKER_01] moliti,

868
00:35:17,739 --> 00:35:19,719
[SPEAKER_01] ako ostanemo začepljeni,

869
00:35:19,719 --> 00:35:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] samo ćemo plutati.

870
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ali naš cilj nije da plutamo,

871
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:25,519
[SPEAKER_01] nego da stvarno dopustimo Krista

872
00:35:25,519 --> 00:35:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] da natopi naša srca.

873
00:35:28,139 --> 00:35:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] I zadnja, moja misao,

874
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] to jest nije moja misao,

875
00:35:33,559 --> 00:35:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] nego ovo što želim

876
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,639
[SPEAKER_01] podijeliti s vama,

877
00:35:36,639 --> 00:35:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] Rastjepan će se isto osjetiti,

878
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:42,639
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo bili na fakultetu,

879
00:35:42,639 --> 00:35:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo toliko dobrih stvari učili i čuli,

880
00:35:45,599 --> 00:35:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali te kasnije to nekako sjedne sve na svoje.

881
00:35:50,039 --> 00:35:52,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ima jedna poznata

882
00:35:52,420 --> 00:35:55,780
[SPEAKER_01] od Karla Ranera od crkvi,

883
00:35:55,780 --> 00:35:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] kada kaže,

884
00:35:57,460 --> 00:36:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] crkva je stara žena

885
00:36:00,619 --> 00:36:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] s mnogim ožiljcima i borama,

886
00:36:03,639 --> 00:36:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali ona je moja majka,

887
00:36:06,099 --> 00:36:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] a majku se ne tuče.

888
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:11,239
[SPEAKER_01] Crkva je moja majka,

889
00:36:11,239 --> 00:36:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] a majku se ne tuče.

890
00:36:13,139 --> 00:36:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] Volite svoju crkvu,

891
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] volite svoju majku,

892
00:36:17,559 --> 00:36:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] čuvajte je,

893
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] liječite je,

894
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] pomažite joj,

895
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:24,340
[SPEAKER_01] budite dio nje,

896
00:36:24,340 --> 00:36:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] a nemojte je tući.

897
00:36:26,219 --> 00:36:28,500
[SPEAKER_01] Amen.

898
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:30,099
[SPEAKER_01] Valja Nisus i Marija.

899
00:36:33,099 --> 00:36:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] I tako si živ

900
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] i tako te osjećaj.

901
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Bog vas blagoslovio.

902
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala.

